title: Elegant Apartment in Innere Stadt
description: Charming 3-bedroom apartment in Vienna's historic Innere Stadt. Features classic Viennese architecture with modern amenities, high ceilings, and a fully-equipped kitchen. Walking distance to St. Stephen's Cathedral and the State Opera.

title: Modern Loft Near Mariahilfer Straße
description: A contemporary loft with an open floor plan, located near Vienna's bustling Mariahilfer Straße shopping district. This 2-bedroom loft features a spacious living area, modern decor, and a rooftop terrace with panoramic city views.
